{"questionId": "ad300285-6ff9-46a9-97ab-7356c9cd2965_4", "correctAnswer": "17", "section": "Math", "steps": [{"title": "Substitute the value x = 144", "content": "Replace $x$ with $144$ in $$f(x) = 5 + \\sqrt{x}.$$ This gives $$f(144) = 5 + \\sqrt{144}.$$"}, {"title": "Compute the result", "content": "Simplify: $$f(144) = 5 + 12 = 17.$$ The answer is <strong>17</strong>."}]}